	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=35651><span id=Guru>Keyeluke</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>679 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.53]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Yes oh yes if you plan to solo you NEED bind wound.&nbsp;&nbsp;Monks who solo use bind wound to get to 50% hp then use mend to get to 75% hp.<br><br>If you want to wait to practice it up (I waited till about lvl 20 or so before I started) because of finances, then stick to groups till then.<br><br>Keyeluke <br>Monk of the Silent Fist, 45th Circle <br>Strange Brew <br>Druzzil Ro&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>Keyeluke<br>Member of Tenacity - Druzzil Ro<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=27415</a></td></td></tr>
